column5: Just got back from a week here. 7/8-7/15 with my boys and brother in law. Had a great time with good weather and plenty of fish to eat! 2nd ownership since 2019, and they are dedicated to getting cabins, boats and things up to date. Good people and hope they make it.Video of the trip...https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KkUc...sBpgx&index=14
